txt.en: 'Now, war-host, watch what happens to dogs!'
'He of Many Colours told us to expect resistance. Good! I will relish this battle.'
'Sharkû claims this place. You and those Angmarim are pests to be removed!'
'These dogs have teeth, but so do men of Dunland!'
'The dogs bite deeply - quickly, fetch one of the leaders to close my wounds!'
'Tear these ruins apart!'
'I would rather be slaughtering the Men of Rohan, but no...I am stuck here amongst you worthless curs!'
'Whip these men like the curs they are and find something for Sharkû!'
'Keep up the work you slugs!'
'We don't stop until He of the many colours is satisfied!'
'Work harder you scum!'
'You slow down and I'll flay the flesh from your backs!'
'Worthless wretches! Work! Work! Work!!!'
'Stop sloughing off!'
'Sharkû does not tolerate failure!'
'Kill them all and I might respect you enough to fight you.'
'Until you defeat me...you shall be my guest.'
'Quickly, I underestimated these curs...to my aid!'
'I see you there, maggots. Besting my brethren.'
'Worthless worms the lot of them! You've done me a favour.'
'Now that I have you close, it is time to die!'
'Free People? Ha! Slaves to masters unseen you are!'
'I warn you fight me toe-to-toe - else I slaughter you without a thought!'
'I will get an uruk leader!'
'Intruders!'
'Saruman speaks true. You are dogs licking at scraps!'
